Deliver consistent campaigns everywhere.










Read The Forrester Wave™: Real-Time Interaction Management, Q2 2017. Learn more ›








What is Adobe Campaign?


It’s a set of solutions that help you personalize and deliver campaigns across all your online and offline channels.





Simplify campaign management.
Manage your data and monitor the performance of your cross-channel campaigns from one place.






Deliver engaging email.

Use personalized, contextual, and real-time email messages to deliver a compelling customer experience.






Automate campaigns.

Use marketing automation to increase your campaign productivity and reduce time to market.












See what Campaign can do.























Build individual profiles based on the actions and interests gathered across marketing channels.
Learn more about integrated customer profiles ›
 
















Intuitively design and automate customer experiences across channels, from one-off campaigns to triggered messages, with a graphically rich interface.
Learn more about cross-channel campaign orchestration ›
 
















Use personalization and well-orchestrated cross-channel marketing strategies to deliver relevant and engaging email experiences.
Learn more about contextual email marketing ›
 
















Deliver one-to-one messages across inbound and outbound channels through a dynamic and centralized offer catalog.
Learn more about real-time interaction management ›
 





































 
 
Combine solutions for better campaigns.

Integrations with Adobe Marketing Cloud core services and solutions such as Adobe Analytics and Experience Manager can improve your Adobe Campaign strategy with deep insights and convenient content management.

 








 
