Products and Services



Products and Services
As a community news digital media, NowNews  releases the most recent, most instant and most fancy self-produced news. We took  the initiative to achieve more value and benefits by integrating the media advantages  and cross-domain below.
 

1.	Products and Services
 
NowNews owns a strong team of independent  writers and editors to produce over 350 self-produced pieces of news, which are  diversified into Finance, Politics, Global economics, Technology,  Entertainment, Style, Shopping, Tourist, etc. In addition, NowNews provides and  exchanges new contents for cooperation news website to form a strong news  network.
 


2.	Intergraded Social Media
       
WeChat QR Code:  
News is now becoming a share of topic.  NowNews provides the important source of information to everyone. We run  facebook fan club, and were the first to cooperate with LINE and WeChat, which  are hottest communication apps, to update news and information. 


3.	Multi-Appliance

  
With the advent of mobile information age, we took the lead in launching NowNews Mobile Web and App. Our daily flow broke 1,5M/day in site wide. And it broke 5M/day in mobile site. In the meanwhile, NowNews is the only media that is available for Mainland China, accounts for 10% of flows.
 1.	NowNews listed NO.14 in Top100 websites by the global leader in measuring the digital world comScore.
 2.	NowNews listed NO.18 in Top100 hottest website in Taiwan in 2014. 
3.	NowNews listed NO.22 in Top100 hottest fan club in Taiwan in 2013. 




 







